                        <p><i class="fa fa-chevron-right"></i> Add ongoing Performance Rewiews into the mix (observation and coaching on a job task)</p>
                        <p><i class="fa fa-chevron-right"></i> Make both types of "review" based on actual, objective, job results measurements</p>
