                                        <h4>Accountability Review</h4>
                                        <p>The formal annual "KPI" Accountability Review.  This is an official documenting of acceptable or unacceptable results, based on the KPI's for the job.  Often this is a document signed by both the employee and manager, and filed in the employee's personnel file.  This is what we think of as the heart of the classic Annual Review.</p>
                        			</div>

